<html lang="zh-CN"><head><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8">
    
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>生成背景图片</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            padding: 20px;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .color-box {
            width: 500px;
            height: 400px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: white;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
        }
        .white {
            background-color: #FFFFFF;
            color: #333;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
        }
        .black {
            background-color: #000000;
        }
        .green {
            background-color: #8ACF00;
        }
        .blue {
            background-color: #0A00AD;
        }
        h1 {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        p {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .instructions {
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>背景图片生成器</h1>
    
    <div class="instructions">
        <p><strong>使用说明：</strong></p>
        <ol>
            <li>右键点击每个颜色框</li>
            <li>选择"另存为图片"或"保存图片"</li>
            <li>将图片保存到images目录</li>
            <li>按照建议的文件名保存</li>
        </ol>
    </div>
    
    <div class="color-box white" id="white-bg">
        白色背景 (brat-bg-white.png)
    </div>
    
    <div class="color-box black" id="black-bg">
        黑色背景 (brat-bg-black.png)
    </div>
    
    <div class="color-box green" id="green-bg">
        绿色背景 (brat-bg-green.png)
    </div>
    
    <div class="color-box blue" id="blue-bg">
        蓝色背景 (brat-bg-blue.png)
    </div>
    
    <script>
        // 添加点击事件，提示用户保存图片
        document.querySelectorAll('.color-box').forEach(box => {
            box.addEventListener('click', function() {
                const color = this.id.split('-')[0];
                alert(`请右键点击此框，选择"另存为图片"，并将其保存为 brat-bg-${color}.png`);
            });
        });
    </script>

 </body></html>